    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;I would suggest you use the SAP Cloud SDK HTTP Client:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;A href="https://sap.github.io/cloud-sdk/docs/js/features/connectivity/http-client" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://sap.github.io/cloud-sdk/docs/js/features/connectivity/http-client&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;as it will support the resolution of destinations out of the box. In BAS you can set the destination in a &lt;A href="https://sap.github.io/cloud-sdk/docs/js/features/connectivity/destinations" target="_self" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;destinations&lt;/A&gt; environment variable and use &lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"&gt;http://&amp;lt;dest-name&amp;gt;.dest&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;in the URL&lt;/P&gt;</content>
